>行为转变的过程总是始于自觉。在你想改变习惯之前，你需要首先了解它。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻074-培养习惯四步法</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB074-%E5%9F%B9%E5%85%BB%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E5%9B%9B%E6%AD%A5%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 21:03:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB074-%E5%9F%B9%E5%85%BB%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E5%9B%9B%E6%AD%A5%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>习惯不会限制自由，它们会创造自由。事实上，没有建立习惯的人往往享有最少的自由。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻073-你的习惯如何塑造你的身份</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB073-%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%A1%91%E9%80%A0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2020 20:28:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB073-%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%A1%91%E9%80%A0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD/</guid><description>改变习惯的最有效方法不是关注你想要达到的目标，而是你想成为谁。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻072-微习惯的力量</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB072-%E5%BE%AE%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2020 21:18:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF/2020-03-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB072-%E5%BE%AE%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F/</guid><description>习惯是自我提高的复利。</description></item></channel></rss>